    <briefdescription>
<para>This file contains the function prototypes, macro definitions and structure definitions for Platform Configuration Register (PCR) operations in the OCP library. </para>    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The PCR module provides APIs for:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Hardware PCR extend and read operations</para></listitem><listitem><para>Software PCR configuration, extend and read operations</para></listitem><listitem><para>PCR event logging and retrieval</para></listitem><listitem><para>Secure state measurement and extension to PCRs</para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para><para><preformatted>
MODIFICATION HISTORY:</preformatted></para><para><preformatted>Ver   Who  Date     Changes
